ygData.messageBody:
I'm 36, my hubby is 32, our friends that we play with every day are 32, 26, 44, and 54. (We all work together during the day and then group up in EQ at nite and weekends. =)  We also have a second group that we interchange players with....my sis-in-law and her friends..all ages 21-24.  I've found on Kane Bayle the average age is much higher than on some of the more populated servers.  And yes, it's a European server, but we're all Americans..... By much higher I guess there just doesn't seem to be as many very young teens or kids on there.  =)  Then again maybe those Europeans are just better behaved! ;)  LOL
 
J
